a:50:{i:1202016;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202016";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:126:"&quot;Oo, oo! Do me!&quot; Ruby excitedly demands, trotting about in place a little. &quot;Do your identify thing on me.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420950120";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209501340";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202038;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202038";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:291:"/me tilts her head to one side. &quot;Err.. I don&#039;t think it works on ponies... it&#039;s more of a inanimate object and plants thing..&quot; She frown. &quot;Not that I&#039;ve tried, but all ponies are said to have latent magic, so I don&#039;t really know how that would work..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420950596";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209506004";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202040;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202040";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:121:"&quot;Wait, do they?&quot; Ruby looks shocked, or concerned. &quot;No they don&#039;t... do they? What do you mean?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420950640";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209506539";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202042;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202042";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:231:"She isn&#039;t wrong either. Unrest&#039;s only true magical sources is duskstone, sunstone, and the neutral field of it throughout the land. Other objects can be created to store this energy, but not a living thing. Or so is said.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420950696";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209507100";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202059;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202059";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:559:"/me seems sure of herself. &quot;Well, yeah.. Unicorns it&#039;s pretty obvious and earth ponies generally have a bond to the earth, strength, but then you have pegasi that can walk on clouds and create weather..&quot; She stops for a moment and looks a bit crestfallen. &quot;No.. I&#039;m thinking of Equestria.. Pegasi can&#039;t control the weather here, can they..&quot; She shakes her head and then looks intently at the young filly, eyes becoming somewhat unfocused for a moment. &quot;Huh..&quot; She snaps back to attention and seems a bit perplexed.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420951518";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209515191";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202060;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202060";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:371:"&quot;Stuff with wings can still move clouds and stuff, yeah. It&#039;s just that it does it by itself anyone so no one really bothers.&quot; She explains. &quot;You are probably thinking of that Eque-whatever place though.&quot;[br]Ruby waits, her smile dropping over a few seconds until finally dispelled by the perplexed expression. [br]&quot;Is something wrong?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420951643";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209516568";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202063;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202063";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:119:"/me shakes her head. &quot;I wouldn&#039;t say so, no.. but I would say your teacher is probably right about you.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420951891";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209518948";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202064;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202064";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:175:"&quot;Oh right, that.&quot; Ruby smiles again, the expression puffing up her cheeks to flaw those freckles some more. &quot;Mejai&#039;s IS really smart with that stuff.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420951955";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209519686";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202066;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202066";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:15:"&quot;Mejai IS*";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420952065";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209520782";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202073;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202073";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:291:"/me taps her beak lightly. &quot;Do you know how she knows that kind of stuff? I think it would be interesting to find someone else that has a similar talent to mine.. I still don&#039;t know very much about it, I didn&#039;t get my cutie mark until I was nearly finished with school..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420952281";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209522855";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202083;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202083";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:135:"&quot;Heh, that&#039;s easy. Mejai&#039;s a giant queen spider.&quot; She says, as if that&#039;s nothing to be concerned about at all.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420952482";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209524955";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202087;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202087";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:118:"/me blanches. She&#039;d seen some curious creatures since coming to Unrest, but never.. &quot;A.. giant spider?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420952656";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209526606";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202096;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202096";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:156:"&quot;Yeah. Mejai is like an art project where someone drew most bits of a spider and then finished with making them a vampire pony.&quot; Ruby sagely nods.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420952817";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209528307";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202104;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202104";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:262:"/me tries really hard to not look distraught, she knows the filly had called this Mejai her temporary mum, but the two mental images weren&#039;t exactly coming together very well. &quot;That&#039;s.. different. I have.. never met someone like that before.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420953198";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209532003";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202107;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202107";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:278:"Ruby frowns a little, taking a small step forward to speak a little more softly to Pixie.[br]&quot;She&#039;s really nice though.. she wouldn&#039;t hurt anyone on purpose. There&#039;s heaps of kids there, and we all love her. She&#039;s not as scary as you think she is.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420953297";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209533105";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202122;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202122";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:127:"/me gives a small smile. &quot;I&#039;m sure it&#039;s just as you say.Things are just.. really different in Unrest, huh?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420953916";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209539199";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202128;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202128";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:272:"Ruby nods again. &quot;Yeah, it&#039;s a lot like that. I just try not to judge anyone unless they&#039;re doing something bad, you know?&quot; She offers. The innocent insight of an older child. &quot;So uhh, do you need to be somewhere or can I keep bothering you?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420953998";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209540009";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202134;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202134";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:122:"/me laughs lightly. &quot;Not particularly. I only really know Dr V, and I&#039;m not working today, so bother away.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420954095";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209540955";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202142;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202142";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:178:"Ruby shuffles about on her hooves for a moment, awkwardly, just kinda looking at the ground. Eventually she looks up, asking: &quot;Do you wanna see the sandfall?&quot; She asks.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420954178";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209541918";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202143;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202143";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:10:"-She asks.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420954186";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209541961";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202148;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202148";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:53:"/me blinks, confused. &quot;The.. the sandfall?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420954357";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209543612";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202150;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202150";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:220:"Ruby smiles again, a little bit. &quot;Yeah, there&#039;s an old broken place not far from the academy. It has a basement balcony sorta thing, and this really neat sandfall. Like a waterfall, but with sand I think.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420954423";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209544366";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202173;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202173";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:192:"/me was a bit leery of secluded places after her last experience in the less inhabited parts of Baribria, but it a child was able to go on her own.. &quot;Sure, why not. Sounds like fun!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420954695";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209546979";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202175;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202175";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:195:"&quot;O-okay!&quot; Ruby&#039;s smile returns in full. Quickly the kid turns and starts merrily trotting along toward the old military district, and within it the old, ruined building apparently.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420954812";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209548257";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202178;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202178";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:111:"/me follows after Ruby, her larger stride making it easy for her to keep up with the filly at a leisurely pace.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420954957";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209549613";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202186;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202186";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:701:"The city around them gets progressively more and more run down as they walk in through toward the old military district. It appears the royalty really did just get up and leave the place, never to return... it almost makes you wonder why.[br]The level of wealth around here is equally as low as the ruined buildings would tell. It&#039;s not quite as happy as Baribria at large, easily classifying as a slum, but all in all a very pleasant one. It&#039;s no Finrest... Pointedly though, there are no Dao here. No beings made of sand that stand as watchful guardians of the city. Creatures with gemstone eyes and shifting bodies. Quite eerie really, and no mouths. They never talk. They simply enforce.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420955190";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209552041";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202188;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202188";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:192:"Ruby leads Crimson_Pixie into the side streets eventually, moving toward the outer wall of the floating city and the ruined buildings there. It is around here that the sandfall is, supposedly.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420955263";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209552772";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202192;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202192";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:156:"/me seems attentive to her surroundings, idly wondering at what point she&#039;d lost some of that self-assuredness of her youth as she followed after Ruby.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420955520";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209555239";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202195;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202195";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:529:"&quot;Gotta be careful here, stuff&#039;s falling apart. You&#039;re light, right?&quot; She idly wonders in Pixie&#039;s direction...[br]A few minutes pass before Ruby and the hippogryph find themselves standing outside the sealed, worn, ornate gates of what probably used to be an estate. The building is in the distance, not far but walled in. It looks like it was lavish once, an echo of a time past.[br]&quot;Lemme open the gate, there&#039;s a hole in the wall over this side.&quot;The filly informs. &quot;Wait here.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420955696";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209557102";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202196;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202196";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:216:"/me &quot;More or less,&quot; she responds. Pixie was relatively lightfooted, but would be able to easily take wing if necessary. Upon reaching the gate, the hippogryph waits patiently as Ruby goes to open said gate.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420955914";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209559183";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202197;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202197";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:430:"It totally blanks Ruby&#039;s mind that Pixie could just fly over, BUT, I&#039;ve yet to state this properly anywhere but Baribria is a no-fly zone. Just as a thing...[br]Ruby disappears behind the corner of the wall only to return a few seconds later on the other side. She offers a cheeky wave before touching her hoof to the button on the inside that causes the gate to slide open. Near-silently too. &quot;There you go~.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420956024";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209560375";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202200;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202200";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:172:"/me moves through the now open gate nimbly, gazing around at her surrounds as she joins the filly once more. &quot;You certainly know your way around, don&#039;t you?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420956144";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209561483";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202201;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202201";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:224:"Ruby giggles softly. &quot;I just have a lot of time on my hooves, that&#039;s all. I wasn&#039;t always in the academy with the other poor kids.&quot; The filly offers. &quot;Come on, the sandfall isn&#039;t far now~.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420956235";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209562484";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202206;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202206";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:70:"/me tails Ruby as she smiles, enjoying the anticipation of the moment.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420956616";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209566198";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202211;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202211";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:1202:"The inside of the estate is quite fanciful if not for the dust and such. There&#039;s all kinds of pretty things in here, though it does appear those most that aren&#039;t nailed down or otherwise difficult to manhandle out of here are missing. The place does feel looted, robbed of its former glory.[br]Surely a noble family must have lived here once, judging by the nicely carved stairs and the impressive (yet unpowered) chandelier. It is as beautiful as it is sad, though it&#039;s hardly the main attraction here...[br]Ruby continues down into the basement level, which is behind a hidden door in the study. What appears to be a book case is, unoriginally, a secret door followed by a forgivingly wide set of stairs. Spooky stuff. How&#039;d she find this again? Moving on.[br]At the bottom of the staircase is the basement, or rather a secondary (and hidden) rumpus room untouched by looters and scamps. There is statuettes, paintings, books, a fanciful chess set of silver and glass among other things. It&#039;s a thief&#039;s wet dream to be honest.[br][br]&quot;Here we are, sandfall is in that room.&quot; She says, pointing to the door on the far side of this already quite impressive room.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420956890";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209569034";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202224;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202224";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:378:"/me seems to marvel at her surrounding, even in it&#039;s present state, the estate spoke of lavishness beyond her tiny apartment. The statuettes and books practically begged her to look them over, but at Ruby draws back the hippogryph&#039;s attention with her words, her gaze turns to follow Ruby&#039;s gesture and Pixie continues on towards the sandfall, whatever it may be.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420957203";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209572062";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202237;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202237";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:860:"Ruby trots on toward the next room then~! In the distance you can hear the sound of sand in the wind, lots of it.[br]&quot;This place is pretty cool, isn&#039;t it?&quot; She smiles as she turns the handle.[br]The door opens to reveal what is essentially a viewing room. A tanning room, also. A lounge with a big glass viewing window the the outside, outside of Baribria itself. Currently though it is sealed, hidden. A cloud of sand swirls about outside the glass, similar sounding to a gentle shower. Light trickles in through the occasional space in the sand cloud, creating a very calming and comforting environment. You&#039;d think someone would know about this by now, it&#039;s a legitimate security risk all things considered, surely... but here it is.[br][br]Ruby proudly walks over to one of the couches and curls up on it, smiling Pixie&#039;s way.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420957666";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209576798";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202253;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202253";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:209:"/me moves to the window, barely touching it with her clawed hand as she gazes outside, watching the sand in fascination. &quot;It&#039;s amazing.. what&#039;s equally so, is that you found such a place..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420957942";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209579447";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202260;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202260";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:182:"&quot;Isn&#039;t it?&quot; Ruby grins. &quot;This place is pretty awesome, and safe. I found it ages ago when I needed a place to say. Now it&#039;s kinda just like my hideout.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420958161";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209581751";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202277;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202277";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:226:"/me explores the room a bit more, before settling on one of the couches. &quot;And what a hideout it is.. I find it a bit of a marvel no one else has stumbled upon the little treasure you have here.. but it&#039;s nice..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420958706";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209587100";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202279;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202279";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:245:"&quot;Yeah, it&#039;s very cozy... I spent about two months here I think. It was alright, better than it could have been.&quot; She sighs a little, playing with a loose thread on the couch with a forehoof.[br]&quot;Is Doctor V good to you?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420958845";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209588591";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202285;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202285";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:384:"/me tilts her head to one side. &quot;Good to me? As an employer I&#039;d say she&#039;s relatively agreeable.. Quiet.. keeps to herself, doesn&#039;t exactly like it when I get too nosey. But she also gives me privileges I wouldn&#039;t have otherwise.. Access to the libraries, working on my own projects whenever there&#039;s nothing to be done at the clinic. Why do you ask?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420959061";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209590648";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202294;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202294";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:107:"Ruby shrugs a little. &quot;Just wondering. I don&#039;t really know what I&#039;m doing.&quot; She admits.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420959314";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209593241";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202301;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202301";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:170:"/me seems thoughtful for a moment and chooses to ask a question she&#039;d held back on earlier. &quot;What about you, Ruby? And.. why is Mejai your temporary mom..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420959745";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209597493";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202306;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202306";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:183:"Ruby sits upright and settles in on the couch again.[br]&quot;I&#039;m at the academy because I&#039;m alone without it. Mejai takes in poor kids and stuff.&quot; She explains simply.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420959840";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209598532";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202315;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202315";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:155:"/me frowns lightly. &quot;Seems like a lot of folks are alone in Unrest.. Not just the lakers like myself, though that&#039;s certainly a part of it.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420960023";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209600272";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202318;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202318";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:140:"Ruby shrugs a little. &quot;My parents aren&#039;t dead though. They&#039;ll come back one day, or I&#039;ll find them.&quot; She dismisses.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420960121";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209601347";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202325;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202325";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11146";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crimson_Pixie";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1049";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:157:"/me smiles warmly. &quot;I&#039;m sure you will.&quot; She stretches out on the couch and sighs lightly. &quot;Makes me wonder how my family is doing..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420960568";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a5213a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209605718";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e84958";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202327;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202327";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:83:"&quot;Well if they&#039;re like you, they&#039;re probably okay.&quot; Ruby offers.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420960818";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209608321";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1202336;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1202336";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"22";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:7:" /scene";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420961512";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14209615257";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}}